I'm Uyi.

a programmer

Hi.

I'm a fullstack javaScript developer with interests in mobile and Artifical Intelligence development. I have a passion for programming and love to create for web and mobile devices.


My Skills.

Javascript

I live the best of both worlds by developing beautiful front end websites and also implementing the sustainable back end logic for the software's server and database.

Python

Swift

Get In Touch.
